{"tid":699490,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"PS II 二級私人秘書公開招聘討論區 (3)","createTime":"2018-06-12T14:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T11:33:39.000Z","uid":133317,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"64a73c49ddbf48bd16ec12277c79b8bf08648a9a","tid":699490,"uid":133317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"2018年二級私人秘書公開招聘計劃<br />\n二級私人秘書公開招聘已於2018年2月1日截止申請。<br />\n<br />\n2018年公開招聘計劃時間表註 1\t<br />\n事項\t時間<br />\n(1) 二級私人秘書職位申請日期 註2\t已於2018年2月1日截止<br />\n(2) 技能測驗 註 3\t2018年3月至2018年6月<br />\n(中文及英文文書處理速度測驗，以及一般商業電腦軟件應用知識測驗，包括Microsoft Office Word 2013及Excel 2013)\t<br />\n(3) 遴選面試 註 4 及《基本法》知識測試 註 5 2018年4月至2018年7月<br />\n(4) 發出第一批聘書\t2018年8月<br />\n(5) 發出遴選面試最後結果 註 6\t2019年1月底"},{"pid":"6de4fa3b0bda6ab55053f58f18d6e654d257e6c0","tid":699490,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:58:30.000Z","msg":"半年"},{"pid":"162473055af5433a5631d2667e994d9db14abe89","tid":699490,"uid":74557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"喊出黎 當日考既基本法得47 之前考有73<br />\n搏衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34388adc5a00f8a73036077ede3028f7f731af71","tid":699490,"uid":182904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"162473055af5433a5631d2667e994d9db14abe89","tid":699490,"uid":74557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:02:49.000Z","msg":"喊出黎 當日考既基本法得47 之前考有73<br />\n搏衰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22913e07594f755d3daf2be5c4ae3d56978590d2","tid":699490,"uid":74557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34388adc5a00f8a73036077ede3028f7f731af71","tid":699490,"uid":182904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"162473055af5433a5631d2667e994d9db14abe89","tid":699490,"uid":74557,"like":1